@startuml
title Focus Timer State Machine
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Ready
Ready --> Running : Start selected duration
Running --> Running : Tick every second
Running --> Completed : remaining = 0
Running --> FinishedEarly : Finish manually
Running --> Reset : app leaves foreground
Completed --> Saving : calculate elapsed minutes
FinishedEarly --> Saving : calculate elapsed minutes
Saving --> Ready : Firestore write succeeds
Saving --> Ready : write fails / show error
Reset --> Ready : clear start time and restore duration
Ready --> Ready : choose 25 / 45 / 60 / 90 min
@enduml
